  <name>Endurance with Surges - 3 - 80min - RPE9-10</name>
  <description>Endurance with Surges — level 3

WARM-UP:
-10min ramp 50%-&gt;65% FTP (RPE 2-3)

MAIN SET:
-4:09 @ 57%-67% FTP (Z2, RPE 2-3, 90-100rpm)
-30s @ 140% FTP (Z6, RPE 9-10, 90-100rpm)
