COOL-DOWN:
-10min spin-down 70%-&gt;50% FTP (RPE 2-3)

HOW TO RIDE IT:
-Easy and conversational the whole way.

DIMENSIONS:
-zones Z2-Z6 · normal cadence · seated · flat/rolling · attack/recover surges

FUEL:
-40-60g carbs/hr.</description>
